

=Description=

"The Findhorn Ecovillage Network founded in 1995 has helped to develop 400 sustainable communities. The Network’s training program (www.Gaiaeducation.net) is helping many thousands of others to get started in countries ranging from China and Japan to the Brazilian slums. These are groups consisting of at least 1,500 people, 50 percent of whom cannot read or write."

